\eventfr Agent (Buyer): 	            human Patient (Item): 		grain, foodSource (Seller): 	human Instrument (Price):	silver, gold, or other valued item
\syntagc The term is used most frequently in the Joseph account in which the food item being sold is grain, the prototypical food of that region.  The term can, however, be used for the purchase of other food items or food in general, in which case the object is more likely to be specifically stated.
