\dfnotes The overall frame for this verb is discernment and wisdom. Since discernment can be applied to a wide number of activities and professional occupations, it is no wonder that the frame is activated in a wide area of domains. What they have in common, though, is their positive stand in the Israelite mindset. The verb |hבין|h* is never used in domains that are negatively valued, such as criminal activities.
