\syntagcc The commentaries (WBC, NICOT, TOTC, KD) and translations indicate three possible interpretations of the phrase |hזִבְחֵי־צֶדֶק|h*, though there is no need to assume that all three instances of the phrase have the same meaning:1. Sacrifices offered according to the law.2. Sacrifices offered by those who were more generally faithful to the law.3. Sacrifices offered in response to God's righteous acts towards his people.The commentaries are divided but, for the most part, give no reasons for their decisions.
