\intro 1. The Meanings of this noun are related to the central meaning 'knowledge', ranging from very weak knowledge (awareness) to strong knowledge.2. The word has different Intrinsic Domains which help to distinguish the different Meanings.3. In the domain of the human body, the word denotes conscious control over body movements (Meaning 1). 4. In the domain of information, the word means 'knowledge' in the sense of familiarity with a something or someone, be it man or God (Meaning 2).5. In the domain of experience, the word 'knowledge' in the sense of experience either in morality or in particular crafts.6. In the domain of wisdom, the word 'knowledge' in the sense of wisdom, insight into life, good judgement.
